#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:8
msgid "Configuring Google Apps as a Single Sign-On (SSO) service"
msgstr "Google Apps를 단일 로그인(SSO) 서비스로 구성하기"

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:10
msgid ""
"Follow these steps to configure Mattermost to use Google as a Single "
"Sign-on (SSO) service for team creation, account creation, and login."
msgstr ""
"팀 생성, 계정 생성 및 로그인을 위한 단일 로그인(SSO) 서비스로 Google을 사용하도록 Mattermost를 구성하려면 다음 단계를 따르세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:14
msgid ""
"The `Google People API <https://developers.google.com/people>`__ has "
"replaced the Google+ API, which was deprecated by Google as of March 7th,"
" 2019 `per their notice <https://developers.google.com/+/api-"
"shutdown>`__."
msgstr ""
"`Google People API <https://developers.google.com/people>`__ 가 Google+ API를 대체했습니다. "
"Google+ API는 2019년 3월 7일부로 Google에 의해 더 이상 사용되지 않게 되었습니다. `공지사항 <https://developers.google.com/+/api-"
"shutdown>`__ 를 참조하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:17
msgid "Step 1: Create OpenID Connect project in Google API Manager"
msgstr "1단계: Google API Manager에서 OpenID Connect 프로젝트 생성하기"

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:19
msgid "Go to Google Cloud Platform."
msgstr "Google Cloud Platform으로 이동하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:21
msgid "Select **Credentials** in the left-hand sidebar."
msgstr "왼쪽 사이드바에서 **Credentials** 를 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:23
msgid "Select **Create Credentials**, then select **OAuth client ID**."
msgstr "**Create Credentials** 를 선택한 다음 **OAuth client ID** 를 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:25
msgid "Select the **Web application** as the application type."
msgstr "애플리케이션 유형으로 **Web application** 을 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:27
msgid ""
"Enter ``Mattermost-<your-company-name>`` as the **Name**, replacing "
"``<your-company-name>`` with the name of your organization."
msgstr ""
"**Name** 으로 ``Mattermost-<your-company-name>`` 을 입력하세요. ``<your-company-name>`` 을 조직의 이름으로 바꾸세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:29
msgid ""
"Under **Authorized redirect URIs**, select **Add URL**, then enter "
"``{your-mattermost-url}/signup/google/complete``. For example: "
"``http://localhost:8065/signup/google/complete``."
msgstr "**Authorized redirect URIs** 아래에서 **Add URL** 을 선택한 다음 ``{your-mattermost-url}/signup/google/complete`` 를 입력하세요. "
"예: ``http://localhost:8065/signup/google/complete``."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:31
msgid "Select **Create**."
msgstr "**Create** 를 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:33
msgid ""
"Copy and paste the **Your Client ID** and **Your Client Secret** values "
"to a temporary location. You will enter these values in the Mattermost "
"System Console."
msgstr "**Your Client ID** 와 **Your Client Secret** 값을 임시 위치에 복사하여 붙여넣으세요. 이 값들은 Mattermost 시스템 콘솔에 입력하게 됩니다."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:46
msgid "Step 2: Enable Google People API"
msgstr "2단계: Google People API 활성화하기"

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:48
msgid ""
"Go to the `Google People API <https://developers.google.com/people>`_, "
"then select **Enable** in the header. This might take a few minutes to "
"propagate through Google's systems."
msgstr "`Google People API <https://developers.google.com/people>`_ 로 이동한 다음 헤더에서 **Enable** 을 선택하세요. Google 시스템에 전파되는 데 몇 분 정도 걸릴 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:51
msgid "Step 3: Configure Mattermost for Google Apps SSO"
msgstr "3단계: Google Apps SSO용 Mattermost 구성하기"

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:53
msgid ""
"Log in to Mattermost, then go to **System Console > Authentication > "
"OpenID Connect**."
msgstr "Mattermost에 로그인한 다음 **시스템 콘솔 > 인증 > OpenID Connect** 로 이동하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:55
msgid "Select **Google Apps** as the service provider."
msgstr "서비스 제공자로 **Google Apps** 를 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:57
msgid ""
"The **Discovery Endpoint** for OpenID Connect with Google Apps is "
"prepopulated with ``https://accounts.google.com/.well-known/openid-"
"configuration``."
msgstr "Google Apps와 함께 사용하는 OpenID Connect의 **Discovery Endpoint** 는 ``https://accounts.google.com/.well-known/openid-configuration`` 으로 미리 채워져 있습니다."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:59
msgid "Paste in the **Client ID** from Google in Mattermost."
msgstr "Google에서 가져온 **Client ID** 를 Mattermost에 붙여넣으세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:61
msgid "Paste in the **Client Secret** from Google in Mattermost."
msgstr "Google에서 가져온 **Client Secret** 을 Mattermost에 붙여넣으세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:63
msgid "Select **Save**."
msgstr "**저장** 을 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/onboard/sso-google.rst:66
msgid ""
"When Mattermost is configured to use OpenID Connect or OAuth 2.0 for user"
" authentication, the following user attribute changes can't be made "
"through the Mattermost API: first name, last name, or username. OpenID "
"Connect or OAuth 2.0 must be the authoritative source for these user "
"attributes."
msgstr "Mattermost가 사용자 인증을 위해 OpenID Connect 또는 OAuth 2.0을 사용하도록 구성된 경우, "
"다음 사용자 속성 변경은 Mattermost API를 통해 수행할 수 없습니다: 이름, 성 또는 사용자 이름. "
"OpenID Connect 또는 OAuth 2.0이 이러한 사용자 속성의 권한 있는 소스여야 합니다."

